<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SQL执行器 - {:C('site_title')}</title>
    <meta name="keywords" content="SQL执行器">
    <meta name="description" content="SQL执行器">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <link href="__PUBLIC__/admin/css/bootstrap.min.css?v=3.3.6" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="__PUBLIC__/admin/css/font-awesome.min.css?v=4.4.0" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="__PUBLIC__/admin/css/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="__PUBLIC__/admin/css/style.min.css?v=4.1.0" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="gray-bg">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper-content animated fadeInRight">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="ibox-title">
                <h5>SQL执行器</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="ibox-content">
            <form action="{:U('Database/Upsql')}" method="post" id="myform" name="myform">
                <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover m-t-md">
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="text-right"><textarea name="sql" id="sql" type="text" class="form-control" rows="5" cols="20"></textarea></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <span style="color:#FF0000">清空所有数据，并且让ID归0：Truncate table 表名</span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <input type="submit" name="submit" value="开始运行" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"> <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button"><i class="fa fa-repeat"></i> 重置</button>　<label>一旦执行后将无法恢复，请确定条件语句正确无误，或者备份好数据库以防万一!</label>
                </form>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
                {__TOKEN__}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="__PUBLIC__/js/jquery.min.js?v=2.1.4"></script>
    <script src="__PUBLIC__/admin/js/bootstrap.min.js?v=3.3.6"></script>
</body>
</html>
